OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FThe main political parties have now
OL,8,Fpublished their general election
OL,9,Fmanifestos.
OL,11,FMost of their plans are national in
OL,12,Fnature, and ITV News has summarised
OL,13,Fthe key points.
OL,15,FWe have looked through the documents
OL,16,Fto find points particularly relevant
OL,17,Fto Cumbria and the South of Scotland.
