OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FThe region is not directly mentioned
OL,8,Fmuch in their manifestos, but the
OL,9,Fparties have strong positions around
OL,10,Fsome of the biggest local issues and
OL,11,Fcontroversies.
OL,13,FShould the proposed coal mine in
OL,14,FWhitehaven go ahead?
OL,16,FThe Conservatives' manifesto does not
OL,17,Fmention the mine, or coal, though they
OL,18,Fhave supported the project in
OL,19,Fgovernment.
