OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FLabour say: "we will not grant new
OL,8,Fcoal licences". It is not clear if
OL,9,Fthis means they would block the
OL,10,FWhitehaven mine if they get into power.
OL,12,FThe Liberal Democrats say they would
OL,13,Fintroduce "a ban on new coal mines".
OL,15,FReform UK say they would "explore
OL,16,Fclean coal mining".
