OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FThe Green Party say their MPs would
OL,8,Fpush the next government to stop all
OL,9,Fnew fossil fuel extraction projects in
OL,10,Fthe UK and to cancel recently issued
OL,11,Flicences, as they believe "it is
OL,12,Fdangerous and reckless to extract more
OL,13,Ffossil fuels in an accelerating
OL,14,Fclimate emergency".
OL,16,FThe SNP say their MPs would demand the
OL,17,FUK government "follow the SNP Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment's lead and commit to no
OL,19,Fsupport for new coal", as they say it
OL,20,Fwould "undermine our action to reach
OL,21,Fnet zero".
