OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FShould there be new nuclear power
OL,8,Fgeneration in West Cumbria or the
OL,9,FSouth of Scotland?
OL,11,FThe Conservatives are promising to
OL,12,F"scale up nuclear power". They say
OL,13,Fthat if they are re-elected, within
OL,14,Fthe first 100 days, they would approve
OL,15,Ftwo new fleets of small modular
OL,16,Freactors, to "create well-paid, high-
OL,17,Fskilled jobs and deliver cheaper,
OL,18,Fcleaner and more secure energy." They
OL,19,Falso say they will "continue laying
OL,20,Fthe groundwork for nuclear projects to
OL,21,Fbe taken forward in Scotland".
