OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FLabour are pledging to "ensure the
OL,8,Flong-term security" of the sector.
OL,9,FThey say new nuclear power stations
OL,10,Fand small modular reactors "will play
OL,11,Fan important role in helping the UK
OL,12,Fachieve energy security and clean
OL,13,Fpower while securing thousands of
OL,14,Fgood, skilled jobs".
OL,16,FThe Liberal Democrats' manifesto does
OL,17,Fnot mention nuclear power.
OL,19,FReform UK say they would "fast-track
OL,20,Fclean nuclear energy" with new small
OL,21,Fmodular reactors, built in Britain.
