OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FThe Green Party say they would stop
OL,8,Fthe development of new nuclear power
OL,9,Fstations, as "nuclear energy is much
OL,10,Fmore expensive and slower to develop
OL,11,Fthan renewables".
OL,13,FThe SNP call on the next UK government
OL,14,Fto "rule out new nuclear plants in
OL,15,FScotland." They argue "the best
OL,16,Fpathway to net zero and secure,
OL,17,Faffordable and clean energy is through
OL,18,Fsignificant growth in renewables,
OL,19,Fstorage, hydrogen and carbon capture".
