OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FShould there be another Scottish
OL,8,FIndependence Referendum?
OL,10,FThe Conservatives argue: "the 2014
OL,11,Fvote was decisive". They accuse the
OL,12,FSNP of remaining "focused on the
OL,13,Fconstitution while Scotland has moved
OL,14,Fon", and say they will "continue to
OL,15,Foppose" any push for another
OL,16,Freferendum on Scottish independence.
