OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FThe SNP's first pledge in their
OL,8,Fmanifesto is to "deliver independence
OL,9,Fto strengthen our economy, tackle the
OL,10,Fcost of living, and bring about a
OL,11,Ffairer country." They claim: "If the
OL,12,FSNP wins a majority of Scottish seats,
OL,13,Fthe Scottish Government will be
OL,14,Fempowered to begin immediate
OL,15,Fnegotiations with the UK Government to
OL,16,Fgive democratic effect to Scotland
OL,17,Fbecoming an independent country".
OL,19,FShould Cumbria have a directly elected
OL,20,Fmayor?
