OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FThe Conservatives say they want to
OL,8,F"empower communities through
OL,9,Fdevolution". If they are elected, they
OL,10,Fsay: "by 2030, every part of England
OL,11,Fthat wants one will have a devolution
OL,12,Fdeal".
OL,14,FLabour say they would "widen
OL,15,Fdevolution to more areas, encouraging
OL,16,Flocal authorities to come together and
OL,17,Ftake on new powers".
