OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FWhat's the best way to stop sewage
OL,8,Fbeing released into our waterways?
OL,10,FThe Conservatives say they have
OL,11,Falready set out an "ambitious" Plan
OL,12,Ffor Water, which includes working with
OL,13,Fthe regulator to further hold water
OL,14,Fcompanies to account, including
OL,15,Fbanning executive bonuses if a company
OL,16,Fhas committed a serious criminal
OL,17,Fbreach.
