OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FLabour say they would put water
OL,8,Fcompanies under special measures to
OL,9,Fclean up waterways, give regulators
OL,10,Fnew powers to block bonuses being
OL,11,Fpaid, and bring criminal charges
OL,12,Fagainst persistent lawbreakers.
OL,14,FThe Liberal Democrats say they would
OL,15,F"end the sewage scandal" by turning
OL,16,Fwater companies into private benefit
OL,17,Fcompanies, banning bonuses for water
OL,18,Fbosses until discharges and leaks end,
OL,19,Fand replacing Ofwat with a "tough" new
OL,20,Fregulator with more powers.
