OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FReform UK do not mention sewage in
OL,8,Ftheir 'Contract' of policies.
OL,10,FThe Green Party argue "the only way to
OL,11,Fend the scandal of our filthy water is
OL,12,Fto end the failed experiment with
OL,13,Fprivatisation and bring the water
OL,14,Fcompanies back into public ownership",
OL,15,Fand say money being extracted by
OL,16,Fshareholders would be invested to fix
OL,17,Fleaks and rebuild infrastructure.
OL,19,FThe SNP manifesto does not mention
OL,20,Fthis issue.
