OL,7,FWhat does the future of farming look
OL,8,Flike?
OL,10,FThe Conservatives are pledging to
OL,11,Fincrease the UK-wide farming budget by
OL,12,F#1bn over the course of the next
OL,13,Fparliament, protect the best
OL,14,Fagricultural land from solar farms,
OL,15,Fand introduce "a legal target and
OL,16,Fadditional investment for food
OL,17,Fsecurity".
