OL,3,CWhere do the parties stand on key
OL,4,Cissues & controversies in the Border
OL,5,Cregion?
OL,7,FLabour say they would "champion
OL,8,FBritish farming whilst protecting the
OL,9,Fenvironment", and set a target for
OL,10,Fhalf of food purchased in the public
OL,11,Fsector to be produced locally or
OL,12,Fcertified to higher environmental
OL,13,Fstandards.
OL,15,FThe Liberal Democrats are pledging to
OL,16,Fintroduce a "holistic and
OL,17,Fcomprehensive" national food strategy
OL,18,Fto "ensure food security, tackle
OL,19,Frising food prices, end food poverty
OL,20,Fand improve health and nutrition".
